Class FontAwesomeIcons

java.lang.Object
io.xlorey.fluxloader.client.core.fonts.FontAwesomeIcons
public class FontAwesomeIcons extends Object
Author: Deknil GitHub: https://github.com/Deknil Date: 07.03.2024 Description: Font Awesome icons codepoints, can be used to render icons with imgui in any place where text can be rendered.

    • _IconRange

      public static final short[] _IconRange
      Array containing the range of FontAwesome icons. The first element is the minimum value, the second element is the maximum value, and the third element is reserved (currently set to 0).
